      <body>
         <head type="date">
            <date when="1804-08-01">August 1, 1804</date>
         </head>
         <div type="entry" xml:id="lc.jrn.1804-08-01.01" n="">
            <sp who="wc">
               <speaker>Clark</speaker>
               <ab>
                  <date/>
               </ab>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">August</hi> the <hi rend="italic">1st 1804</hi>    a fair morning, Sent out two men after the horses &amp; one back to examine if the Indians have been there,<ref target="n05080101" n="1"/> [<hi rend="italic">blank</hi>] Beever Cought last night, the air is Cool and pleasing</p>
               <p>
                  <table rows="4" cols="6">
                     <head>Equal altitudes &amp; magnetic Azmoth</head>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">azmth</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">
                           <hi rend="center">altd.</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">Time</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">      m     s</cell>
