                     </row>
                  </table>
               </p>
               <p>             
The Altitude given 68° 47' 15"</p>
               <p>
The Indians not yet arrived    we fear Something amiss with our Messinger or them.</p>
            </sp>
         </div>
         <div type="entry" xml:id="lc.jrn.1804-08-01.03" n="">
